des:
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off the device. There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo. 

After connecting Alexa to your Perfect IoT products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Perfect IoT" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Perfect IoT account in our "Perfect IoT" app;
(3). You need to have some Perfect IoT devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our “Perfect IoT" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Perfect IoT" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Perfect IoT" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Perfect IoT", and you'll be navigated to Perfect IoT login page;
(9). Input your Perfect IoT account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on light"
“Alexa, turn off light"
